  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/01/30/bing-food-and-drink-windows-phone/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/b34c7f145cbf4c604f5349e0a49a42bd/bing-food-and-drink-windows-phone.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nMicrosoft 再次吧 Windows 跟 Windows Phone 的距离拉近，他们继为 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Windows81/\">Windows 8.1</a> 开发 Bing Food &amp; Drink 之后，又为了 Window Phone 8 开发了一个一样的 app。WP8 版的 Bing Food &amp; Drink 目前正处于 beta 阶段，跟桌面版一样，它除了可以让用户找餐厅和食谱之外，还可以建立食材购物清单。更好的是，桌面版和手机版上的信息是可以同步的，而且可跟其他用户分享。大家对食有兴趣的话，不妨下载到自己的 Windows Phone 8 手机试试。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/30/bing-food-and-drink-windows-phone/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/bing-food-drink-beta/cc512389-0456-430f-876b-704b17317de2?signin=true\">Windows Phone Store</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/31/bing-food-and-drink-windows-phone/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20820034/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/31/bing-food-and-drink-windows-phone/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
